simple meteorjs app - updates stock values in real time as fed by any user on any client

what's in it?

1. creating mongo collection
2. user controls and underlying Meteor code for adding document in the mongo db collection
3. using Meteor.call to call the method which inserts document in mongodb collection, hence, no client side database insertion code
4. uses twitter bootstrap - in css file
5. uses d3js added as meteor package
6. a stub d3js line chart with test data 
7. jquery is also added meteor package

